Hi Ms. Shika. Thank you for reaching out so promptly. I am sorry for my late reply. It wasn't intentional. 

I am an exchange student coming from Canada. My host university is University College London (UCL). Proximity to the campus would be ideal for me.

I plan on staying for about 5 months. I would like to move in around August 18 (so moving out would be around January 18). 
At the very least, I would need a place to stay for approximately 2 weeks (from August 18 to September 1st) while I look for a flat.

My budget ranges from 800¬£ to 950¬£, though I can stretch a little for the right place. However, I would prefer to keep the costs as low as possible. 

My preference is for a private room with a private bathroom; nevertheless, I can consider a private room with a shared bathroom (female-only due to religious reasons).

I am grateful for your support. 

Thank you very much,
-Aisha
